### ── Codelab 03 — Paginación, transacciones y validaciones ──────────

### 1. Listar sin paginación (todos los clientes)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cliente-service/clientes
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Página 0 (primeros 4 clientes)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cliente-service/clientes/page/0
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Página 1 (clientes 5-8)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cliente-service/clientes/page/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Página 2 (clientes 9-12)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cliente-service/clientes/page/2
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Página que no existe -> content vacío, totalElements correcto
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cliente-service/clientes/page/100
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. POST inválido — nombre vacío, email inválido, region nula -> 400 Bad Request
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cliente-service/clientes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "",
  "apellido": "",
  "email": "no-es-email",
  "region": null
}

###

### 7. POST válido -> 201 Created
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cliente-service/clientes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Donald",
  "apellido": "Knuth",
  "email": "knuth@stanford.edu",
  "foto": "knuth.jpg",
  "region": { "id": 3 }
}

###

### 8. GET por ID existente -> 200 OK
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cliente-service/clientes/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 9. GET por ID que no existe -> 404 Not Found
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cliente-service/clientes/999
Accept: application/json

###

### 10. PUT válido — actualizar cliente -> 201 Created
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cliente-service/clientes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Linus",
  "apellido": "Benedict Torvalds",
  "email": "linus@kernel.org",
  "foto": "linus-updated.jpg",
  "region": { "id": 4 }
}

###

### 11. PUT inválido — email con formato incorrecto -> 400 Bad Request
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cliente-service/clientes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Linus",
  "apellido": "Torvalds",
  "email": "linus-sin-arroba",
  "region": { "id": 4 }
}

###

### 12. DELETE existente -> 204 No Content
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cliente-service/clientes/12
Accept: application/json

###

### 13. Listar regiones
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cliente-service/clientes/regiones
Accept: application/json

###
